5
00:00:58,480 --> 00:01:02,280
Full of loneliness and misery
and suffering and unhappiness.

6
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:04,480
And it's all over much too quickly.

7
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:09,680
The other important joke for me is one
that's usually attributed to Groucho Marx.

8
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:14,200
<i>I think it appears originally in Freud's
Wit and its Relation to the Unconscious.</i>

9
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:18,480
