15
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:39,200
That's about the worst
you can say about me.

16
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:41,480
I think I'm gonna get better as I get older.

17
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:44,200
I think I'm gonna be
the balding virile type,

18
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:48,000
as opposed to, say,
the distinguished grey, for instance.

19
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:52,280
Unless I'm one of those guys with
saliva dribbling out of his mouth,

20
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:55,400
