25
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:12,680
A year ago we were... in love, you know.

26
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:17,480
And... It's funny... I'm not a morose type.
I'm not a depressive character.

27
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:19,280
I... I... You know...

28
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,680
I was a reasonably happy kid, I guess.

29
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:24,800
I was brought up in Brooklyn
during World War II.

30
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:29,080
He's been depressed.
