47
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,800
<i>I have a hyperactive imagination.</i>

48
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:28,200
<i>My mind tends to jump around a little.</i>

49
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:31,480
<i>I have some trouble
