50
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:34,080
<i>My father ran the bumper car concession.</i>

51
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,480
<i>There he is.</i>

52
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,000
<i>And there I am.</i>

53
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:40,880
<i>I used to get my aggression out
