58
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:01,280
<i>I always thought
my schoolmates were idiots.</i>

59
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:03,880
<i>Melvyn Greenglass. His fat little face.</i>

60
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:07,400
<i>And Henrietta Farrell.
Just Miss Perfect all the time.</i>

61
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:10,680
<i>And Ivan Ackerman.
Always the wrong answer. Always.</i>

62
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,800
Seven and three is nine.

63
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:15,880
<i>Even then, I knew they were just jerks.</i>

64
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:19,080
<i>In 1942 I had already discovered women.</i>

65
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,680
He kissed me! He kissed me!

66
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:27,200
